                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>Due to the press of time, neither the Seventh Session of the
                                Commission on Human Rights nor the Thirteenth Session of the
                                Economic and Social Council was able to address the question of
                                self-determination.</p>
